001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.Entity;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.*;
005import org.biopax.paxtools.util.BPCollections;
006import org.biopax.paxtools.util.IllegalBioPAXArgumentException;
007
008import java.util.Set;
009
010
011public class ExperimentalFormImpl extends L3ElementImpl implements ExperimentalForm
012{
013
014        private Entity experimentalFormEntity;
015        private Set<ExperimentalFormVocabulary> experimentalFormDescription;
016        private Set<EntityFeature> experimentalFeature;
017
018        /**
019         * Constructor.
020         */
021        public ExperimentalFormImpl()
022        {
023                this.experimentalFormDescription = BPCollections.I.createSafeSet();
024                this.experimentalFeature = BPCollections.I.createSafeSet();
025        }
026
027        //
028        // BioPAXElement interface implementation
029        //
030        ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
031
032        public Class<? extends ExperimentalForm> getModelInterface()
033        {
034                return ExperimentalForm.class;
035        }
036
037        public Set<ExperimentalFormVocabulary> getExperimentalFormDescription()
038        {
039                return experimentalFormDescription;
040        }
041
042        public void addExperimentalFormDescription(ExperimentalFormVocabulary experimentalFormType)
043        {
044                if(experimentalFormType != null)
045                        this.experimentalFormDescription.add(experimentalFormType);
046        }
047
048        public void removeExperimentalFormDescription(ExperimentalFormVocabulary experimentalFormType)
049        {
050                if(experimentalFormType != null)
051                        this.experimentalFormDescription.remove(experimentalFormType);
052        }
053
054        public Entity getExperimentalFormEntity()
055        {
056                return experimentalFormEntity;
057        }
058
059        public void setExperimentalFormEntity(Entity experimentalFormEntity)
060        {
061                if(experimentalFormEntity == null) {
062                        this.experimentalFormEntity = null;
063                } else if(PhysicalEntity.class.isAssignableFrom(experimentalFormEntity.getClass())
064                || Gene.class.isInstance(experimentalFormEntity)) {
065                this.experimentalFormEntity = experimentalFormEntity;
066        } else {
067            throw new IllegalBioPAXArgumentException(
068                    "Argument type is not yet supported: "
069                    + experimentalFormEntity.getModelInterface());
070        }
071        }
072
073    public Set<EntityFeature> getExperimentalFeature()
074    {
075        return experimentalFeature;
076    }
077
078    public void addExperimentalFeature(EntityFeature experimentalFeature)
079    {
080        if(experimentalFeature != null)
081                this.experimentalFeature.add(experimentalFeature);
082    }
083    
084    public void removeExperimentalFeature(EntityFeature experimentalFeature)
085    {
086        if(experimentalFeature != null)
087                this.experimentalFeature.remove(experimentalFeature);
088    }
089}
